categories: Category:Jedi trainees of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: Orth Quane was a male Human Jedi Padawan who served the fledgling Jedi Order during its first days on the planet Tython. A devotee of Jedi Master Rajivari, Quane and several other apprentices abandoned the Order to follow Master Rajivari in his attempts to destroy an Order he saw as plagued by mediocrity.
